    <strong>(b) Dual Aspect Concept:</strong> Every transaction has <span class="kt">TWO aspects — a debit and a credit</span>. Foundation of Double Entry System (Luca Pacioli, 15th century Italy).
    <div class="formula">Assets = Liabilities + Capital
Every transaction affects at least TWO accounts in opposite directions</div>
