    <strong>(c) Accrual:</strong> Revenue recognised when earned; expense when incurred — regardless of cash. Covered in Dec 2025 Q1(d).<br><br>
    <strong>(d) Matching:</strong> Revenues and costs of same period matched. Only cost of goods SOLD matched against sales. Covered in Dec 2024 Q1(c).
